</nav>

<header class="hero wrap">
  <div class="eyebrow">VUS Đông Sài Gòn — Teaching in Dĩ An</div>
  <h1>Twenty minutes from the chaos.<br>A world away from it.</h1>
  <p class="lede">Dĩ An sits 18km northeast of Ho Chi Minh City — close enough for a Saturday in District 1, calm enough to call home on a Tuesday night.</p>
  <div class="hero-cta">
    <a href="#support" class="btn">See teaching packages in Dĩ An</a>
    <a href="#overview" class="btn ghost">Explore the area ↓</a>
  </div>

  <div class="stat-strip">
    <div><div class="num">18 km</div><div class="lbl">Northeast of HCMC, formerly part of Bình Dương</div></div>
    <div><div class="num">20–45 min</div><div class="lbl">By train or metro+bus to central HCMC</div></div>
    <div><div class="num">−47.2%</div><div class="lbl">Average rent vs. central HCMC</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="route">
    <div class="route-label">Your commute, mapped</div>
    <div class="route-line">
      <div class="route-stop"><div class="pin"></div><div class="city">District 1, HCMC</div></div>
      <div class="route-stop"><div class="pin"></div><div class="mode">Train</div><div class="time">20–30 min</div></div>
      <div class="route-stop"><div class="pin"></div><div class="mode">Metro + Bus</div><div class="time">30–45 min</div></div>
      <div class="route-stop"><div class="pin"></div><div class="mode">Car</div><div class="time">45–60 min</div></div>
      <div class="route-stop"><div class="pin"></div><div class="mode">Motorbike</div><div class="time">1–1.5 hr</div></div>
      <div class="route-stop"><div class="pin"></div><div class="city">Dĩ An</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- OVERVIEW -->
<section id="overview">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Overview</span>
      <h2>Two speeds, one neighborhood</h2>
      <p>Dĩ An isn't one single feel — it's a pair of rhythms living side by side, and most teachers find theirs within the first few weeks.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="twocol">
      <div class="feel-card">
        <span class="tag">Outer Dĩ An</span>
        <h3>Spacious &amp; modern</h3>
        <p>Wider roads, newer developments, and more open space create a comfortable, less crowded urban environment — while cafés and daily conveniences stay close at hand.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feel-card">
        <span class="tag">Inner Dĩ An</span>
        <h3>Local &amp; authentic</h3>
        <p>Traditional neighborhoods, long-established shops, and a slower, community-based rhythm. This is where Dĩ An's local character runs deepest.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pace-bar">
      <div><h4>By day</h4><p>Busy and energetic, especially around markets, schools, and commercial streets.</p></div>
      <div><h4>By evening</h4><p>Noticeably calmer and quieter than central HCMC — daily life feels more relaxed once class is over.</p></div>
      <div><h4>Living costs</h4><p>Generally 10–15% lower than HCMC overall, with rent the biggest gap.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TESTIMONIALS (template) -->
<section class="tight alt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Teacher Voices</span>
      <h2>Why I chose Dĩ An</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="testi-note">⚠ TEMPLATE — replace with real quotes, names, and photos from current Dĩ An teachers before publishing.</div>
