      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DAILY LIFE -->
<section id="daily">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Daily Life</span>
      <h2>Your 8–5, and your 5–9</h2>
      <p>What teaching looks like in Dĩ An — and what's waiting for you once the last class ends.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="day-split">
      <div class="day-block">
        <h3>Your 8–5</h3>
        <div class="big">Teaching in Dĩ An</div>
        <p class="sub">A short, predictable commute either way — most teachers are home within 30–45 minutes of their last class, with motorbikes the most common way to get around.</p>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="h">Getting around</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Outer areas: wider roads, easy to navigate</li>
              <li>Inner areas: more truck traffic, extra care needed</li>
              <li>Ride-hailing apps work well while settling in</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="h">Healthcare</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Local hospitals &amp; clinics throughout Dĩ An</li>
              <li>International hospitals nearby in Thủ Đức, Thuận An, Thủ Dầu Một</li>
              <li>Pharmacies widely available</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="day-block">
        <h3>Your 5–9</h3>
        <div class="big">Living local after class</div>
        <p class="sub">Quieter than central HCMC, but never short on the essentials — and a malls-and-markets mix that covers most of what you'll need.</p>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="h">Food &amp; cafés</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Affordable Vietnamese, Korean &amp; Chinese options</li>
              <li>International chains inside shopping malls</li>
              <li>Modern coffee chains &amp; relaxed beer gardens</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="h">Evenings &amp; weekends</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Quieter nightlife — local beer gardens, BBQ, karaoke</li>
              <li>Spacious gyms, football &amp; pickleball courts</li>
              <li>Parks &amp; pagodas within 20–30 min of the center</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- COST & HOUSING -->
<section id="cost" class="alt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Cost &amp; Housing</span>
      <h2>What your salary actually buys</h2>
      <p>The same paycheck stretches further in Dĩ An. Here's the gap, by category, against central HCMC.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cost-card">
      <div class="bar-legend">
        <span><i style="background:#C9D2C1"></i> Central HCMC</span>
        <span><i style="background:var(--pine)"></i> Dĩ An</span>
      </div>

      <div class="cost-row">
        <div class="top"><span class="label">Rent</span><span class="delta">−47.2%</span></div>
        <div class="bartrack"><div class="hcmc"></div><div class="dian" style="width:52.8%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <div class="top"><span class="label">Groceries</span><span class="delta">−15.3%</span></div>
        <div class="bartrack"><div class="hcmc"></div><div class="dian" style="width:84.7%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row">
